[SPEAKER_03] Je, je.

387
00:36:45,880 --> 00:36:45,940
[SPEAKER_03] Je, je.

388
00:36:45,940 --> 00:36:46,440
[SPEAKER_03] Je, je.

389
00:36:46,440 --> 00:36:46,880
[SPEAKER_03] 22.

390
