575
00:52:33,539 --> 00:52:35,199
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su to učinili,

576
00:52:35,199 --> 00:52:38,099
[SPEAKER_00] zato je ovih je više.

577
00:52:38,099 --> 00:52:40,139
[SPEAKER_00] Oni pra nje moraju biti korektni.

578
00:52:40,139 --> 00:52:42,039
[SPEAKER_00] Znamo da je crkva Austrija ušla

579
00:52:42,039 --> 00:52:43,039
