580
00:52:43,039 --> 00:52:44,500
[SPEAKER_00] Vidili smo šta je

581
00:52:44,500 --> 00:52:46,460
[SPEAKER_00] kardinal Šenborn radio u Beću,

582
00:52:46,460 --> 00:52:47,360
