585
00:52:52,659 --> 00:52:55,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ali naravno da će posljedice biti

586
00:52:55,500 --> 00:52:57,199
[SPEAKER_00] također teške tu, sigurno.

587
00:52:57,199 --> 00:53:00,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ja bi vam se rado i pridružio

588
00:53:00,920 --> 00:53:01,980
[SPEAKER_00] prvim subotama,

589
00:53:01,980 --> 00:53:03,980
[SPEAKER_00] ali sam uvijek na putu.

590
00:53:03,980 --> 00:53:06,179
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ne, ne.

591
00:53:06,179 --> 00:53:06,960
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ja bi,

592
00:53:06,960 --> 00:53:08,920
[SPEAKER_00] imam želju i stvarno gledam,

593
00:53:08,920 --> 00:53:11,480
[SPEAKER_00] kad mi se rodi djete ću konačno biti doma.

594
00:53:11,619 --> 00:53:12,820
[SPEAKER_00] znači mi vikendima imamo

595
00:53:12,820 --> 00:53:14,059
[SPEAKER_00] duhovne obnove,

596
00:53:14,059 --> 00:53:16,039
[SPEAKER_00] sad baš za uskrs je termin,

597
00:53:16,039 --> 00:53:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] preporučam u molitvu isto.

598
00:53:18,000 --> 00:53:20,519
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da ću onda biti mjesec dana

599
00:53:20,519 --> 00:53:22,400
[SPEAKER_00] konačno malo doma.

600
00:53:22,400 --> 00:53:24,400
[SPEAKER_00] Uglavnom imamo uvijek vikendima

601
00:53:24,400 --> 00:53:25,280
[SPEAKER_00] duhovne obnove,

602
00:53:25,280 --> 00:53:25,800
[SPEAKER_00] snimanja.

603
00:53:25,800 --> 00:53:28,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ovaj vikend imam i promociju filma.

604
00:53:28,860 --> 00:53:30,159
[SPEAKER_00] to je na večer u šest,

605
00:53:30,159 --> 00:53:31,360
[SPEAKER_00] u sesretama u Kinu,

606
00:53:31,360 --> 00:53:33,199
[SPEAKER_00] u isto jednoj božoj intervenciji

607
00:53:33,199 --> 00:53:33,900
[SPEAKER_00] u Konjicu,

608
00:53:33,900 --> 00:53:35,719
[SPEAKER_00] jel ima neko iz Konjica ovdje

609
00:53:35,719 --> 00:53:36,440
[SPEAKER_00] koje je porijeklo.

610
00:53:36,440 --> 00:53:40,139
[SPEAKER_00] Tri sela,

611
00:53:40,139 --> 00:53:41,659
[SPEAKER_00] na ulazu u grad Konjic,

612
00:53:41,659 --> 00:53:42,480
[SPEAKER_00] koja nisu pala.

613
00:53:42,480 --> 00:53:43,820
[SPEAKER_00] Isto je omjer bio sličan

614
00:53:43,820 --> 00:53:44,659
[SPEAKER_00] kao i na Malti,

615
00:53:44,659 --> 00:53:45,739
[SPEAKER_00] znači, tri korpusa,

616
00:53:45,739 --> 00:53:46,860
[SPEAKER_00] na jedan bataljončić.

617
00:53:46,860 --> 00:53:48,760
[SPEAKER_00] Uspio sam i iz zapovjednika

618
00:53:48,760 --> 00:53:49,679
[SPEAKER_00] vidjeti da su imali

619
00:53:49,679 --> 00:53:50,800
[SPEAKER_00] Božju pomoć,

620
00:53:50,800 --> 00:53:51,360
[SPEAKER_00] ne odmah,

621
00:53:51,360 --> 00:53:51,820
[SPEAKER_00] naravno,

622
00:53:51,820 --> 00:53:53,340
[SPEAKER_00] jer takva je tematika,

623
00:53:53,340 --> 00:53:55,039
[SPEAKER_00] radimo taj digitalni žrtvoslov

624
00:53:55,039 --> 00:53:56,059
[SPEAKER_00] hrvatskog naroda

625
00:53:56,059 --> 00:53:58,519
