00:54:57,420 --> 00:54:59,400
[SPEAKER_04] jirna i srpske postolite.

676
00:54:59,860 --> 00:55:01,619
[SPEAKER_04] tamo su i dočetali

677
00:55:01,619 --> 00:55:03,019
